Definition: any of numerous marine fishes whose elongated spiny body can inflate itself with water or air to form a globe
Example: several species contain a potent nerve poison; closely related to spiny puffers
Synonyms: verb, change, puff, pufferfish, blowfish, globefish, plectognath, family_Tetraodontidae, m, any, of, numerous, marine, fishes, whose, elongated, spiny, body, can, inflate, itself, with, water, or, air, to, form, a, globe, several, species, contain, potent, nerve, poison, closely, related, puffers
Category: noun.animal
